# CODEOWNERS for moses-app-catalog
#
# Rules:
# - Schema, scripts, and CI are owned by the catalog maintainers — no
#   contributor can change validation or signing rules without explicit
#   review by the maintainer team.
# - The contents of apps/<slug>/ are co-owned by the catalog maintainers
#   (security/compliance review) and the listing's own maintainers (technical
#   accuracy). The per-listing CODEOWNERS line below is added when a listing
#   is first merged.

# Default owner — every PR touching anything not otherwise matched goes to
# the catalog maintainers.
*                                    @moses-platform/catalog-maintainers

# Schema, scripts, CI: maintainers only.
/schema/                             @moses-platform/catalog-maintainers
/scripts/                            @moses-platform/catalog-maintainers
/.github/                            @moses-platform/catalog-maintainers
/CONTRIBUTING.md                     @moses-platform/catalog-maintainers
/GOVERNANCE.md                       @moses-platform/catalog-maintainers
/SECURITY.md                         @moses-platform/catalog-maintainers
/README.md                           @moses-platform/catalog-maintainers
/LICENSE.md                          @moses-platform/catalog-maintainers
/CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md                  @moses-platform/catalog-maintainers
/Makefile                            @moses-platform/catalog-maintainers
/package.json                        @moses-platform/catalog-maintainers

# index.json is generated by CI; nobody should edit it by hand. Keeping it
# under maintainer ownership so any drive-by edit is caught in review.
/index.json                          @moses-platform/catalog-maintainers
/signatures/                         @moses-platform/catalog-maintainers

# Per-listing owners are appended below as listings are merged. Format:
# /apps/<slug>/                      @gh-handle1 @gh-handle2 @moses-platform/catalog-maintainers
